Title: 14.1 Built-In Function and Operator Reference
14.7 Date and Time Functions
Description: Return the day of the year (1-366)

Returns the day of the year for
          date, in the range
          1 to 366. Returns
          NULL if date is
          NULL.

Press CTRL+C to copy mysql> SELECT DAYOFYEAR('2007-02-03');
        -> 34
